### Core Location Operations Test File
### Test the basic location functionality including geocoding and search

### 1. Geocode Address - Convert address to coordinates
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "address": "123 Main Street, New York, NY",
  "country_code": "US"
}

###

### 2. Geocode Address - International address
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "address": "10 Downing Street, London",
  "country_code": "GB"
}

###

### 3. Geocode Address - Without country code
